面有很多人在那里随便立法，他们提出的对工商界的要求，比对国家机关和国家企业的要求都高，如按这些要求衡量，我们粮食部也是违法的。"},{"id":"55a3c545e5","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e","index":7,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指章乃器在1955年10月27日给毛泽东的信后附的关于教条主义在民主党派中的表现的专题反映等材料。"}],"contents":[{"id":"894868eac7","type":"title","text":"对章乃器\"来信的批语和复信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"d3ce570891","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、陈、邓、彭真阅，退毛章乃器的信","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"24623198dc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"01095b667c","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十九日陆定一、陈伯达阅，退毛。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"28d1b6a1cf","type":"paragraph","text":"三","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"86752dc6a7","type":"paragraph","text":"此信的主要目的在这一段，意思是说，我们对资产阶级的清规戒律太多了。m","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"a498be38cd","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"55a3c545e5","type":"paragraph","text":"周、陈、彭真、李维汉、徐冰阅，退毛。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"6ffa0ed4e7","type":"paragraph","text":"章乃器的信，值得一看。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"e1455d39f0","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"9982e9b31e","type":"paragraph","text":"乃器部长：","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"1af5812d10","type":"paragraph","text":"前后两信均已收到阅悉。感谢通知我这些情状和你的意见。干部中的片面观点总是会有的，问题是好好帮助他们学会实事求是全面分析的方法。附件“还来不及看，待看后奉还。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"9139a57287","type":"subtitle","text":"祝好！","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e2ad354f3e"},{"id":"67b9971aa9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":13,"p